title: New Jersey Pinelands National Reserve: Current Conditions
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Current Conditions             Alerts & Conditions         Alerts    Caution        If you have been redirected from the New Jersey Coastal Heritage Trail Route  Alert 1 , Severity ,caution ,, If you have been redirected from the New Jersey Coastal Heritage Trail Route  You were redirected to this site from the New Jersey Coastal Heritage Trail Route because of a sunset clause in the Trail's federal legislation, the NPS lost its legislative authority to manage the trail after  9-30-2011. more
